Dust Suppression and Road Stabilization Specialists

About Us

Ihobe International has established over 10 years of experience within the dust suppression and road stabilization industry. Our company footprint has extended a range of geographic locations including the Democratic Republic of Congo, South Africa, Zambia, Mali, Sierra Leone, and Madagascar.

Ihobe International is an eco-friendly company with strong ethical values in the context of health, safety and environmental protocol. The company focuses primarily on dust suppression and road stabilization of haul roads (also including secondary and community roads). The companys core value is to maximize productivity within the mining industry while ensuring environmental sustainability, health and safety and social welfare protocols are adhered to.
